  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b85\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0bb5 \u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0baf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bbe",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "China justifies its warship going to Sri Lanka, a foreign country of India",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "While India has objected to the visit of a Chinese ship to Sri Lanka's southern port, China has said that relevant parties should refrain from interfering in legitimate maritime activities.",
        "India fears that China may use the Sri Lankan leased Ambantota port built by China to set up a military base in its backyard.",
        "Revinitive Eicon's ship data shows that the Chinese research ship Yuan Wang is bound for Ambantota Port and will arrive at the port on the 11th. The Chinese ship will visit Sri Lanka as Sri Lanka faces an unprecedented economic crisis in the region in seven decades.",
        "This year alone, India has given $4 billion in aid to China.",
        "At a press conference on Thursday, an Indian External Affairs Ministry spokesperson said India is monitoring the visit of the Chinese ship as New Delhi defends its economic security interests.",
        "Reuters had reported that India had already expressed its verbal objection to Sri Lanka over the Chinese ship's visit.",
        "China's Ministry of Foreign Affairs has responded to Reuters' question about this and said that China has always used the freedom of the high seas legally.",
        "China's Ministry of Foreign Affairs has stated in a statement that China expects relevant parties to properly observe and report on China's maritime scientific research activities and that they will refrain from interfering in normal and legitimate maritime activities.",
        "Relations between the two countries have been strained since two years ago in which 20 Indian and 4 Chinese soldiers were killed in clashes between Chinese and Indian troops in Ladakh and both sides have deployed large numbers of troops along the border.",
        "Foreign defense analysts have described the Yuan Wang 5 as China's most advanced missile surveillance ship, noting that the ship is capable of tracking the launch of rockets and intercontinental ballistic missiles.",
        "The Pentagon said in its statement that the ship is operated by the strategic support forces of the Chinese military."
      ],
